    <h2><a href="docs#install-it">Install</a></h2>

Quick installation instructions.

```bash
npm i -D mdsvex
```

```bash
yarn add --dev mdsvex
```

  </div>
  <div class="box use">
    <h2><a href="docs#use-it">Use</a></h2>

Add mdsvex to your project

```js
svelte({
  extensions: [
    '.svelte',
    '.svx'
  ],
  preprocess: mdsvex(config)
})
```
